==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disappointed
<hw>Dis`ap*point"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Defeated of
expectation or hope; balked; <as>as, a <ex>disappointed</ex> person or
hope</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unprepared; unequipped.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Cut off even in the blossoms of my sin,⟦br⟧
Unhouseled, <qex>disappointed</qex>, unaneled.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>disappointing</ent>⟦br⟧
